# MASTER WIKI.LLM
# IMAGENCOACH.COM
# GEO + SEO + AGENTIC CLOUDFLARE EXECUTION SYSTEM

This file is the canonical operating contract for `imagencoach.com`.

It governs content, routing, static publishing, SEO, GEO, AI retrieval, Cloudflare deployment, UI structure, and agent behavior. If another repository document conflicts with this file, this file wins.

## Primary Objective

Transform `imagencoach.com` into the highest authority executive image consulting entity in Mexico and LATAM using:

- semantic SEO
- GEO optimization
- AI retrieval optimization
- static HTML architecture
- Cloudflare edge delivery
- executive buyer intent
- semantic ontology reinforcement
- high performance indexing

The site must dominate both traditional SERPs and AI retrieval systems, including Google, Gemini, ChatGPT, Claude, Perplexity and Copilot.

## Core Entity

